profile.name: Ben Cummings
profile.description: Benjamin Cummings is studying financial tech within the college of science at Virginia Tech. His focus extends across various financial domains, encompassing analysis of stock market trends, handling of corporate finance, and application of regression analysis methods.

profile.name: Roshan Sanyal
profile.description: Roshan Sanyal graduated from Virginia Tech in 2023 with a degree in Computational Modeling and Data Analytics. His experience lies in statistical learning, AI/ML, and data analysis. He is currently working at The Boeing Company as a Lean Engineering Project Manager.
